<paragraph blockId="13.[264,1322,1803,1869]" lastBlockId="14.[264,1323,284,390]" lastPageId="14" lastPageNumber="15" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
DIAGNOSIS: In general appearance similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Knight" authorityYear="1973" box="[850,1088,1804,1829]" class="Insecta" family="Myerslopiidae" genus="Myerslopia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="magna" subSpecies="scabrata">
